Turkana Governor Josephat Nanok has praised women for starting an initiative to ensure peaceful campaigns. He said the initiative is timely and encouraged the women to pass the message to leaders across the political divide. Nanok on Saturday addressed the Turkana Women for Peace in Lodwar when they held a peaceful march to call for peace during campaigns. He condemned the violence witnessed during last month s Kalokol ward by-election and the attack on MCA Josphat Ekeno s home.